<div class='media__message'>
<h4 class='h12 talk-link__speaker'>스콧 딘스모어(Scott Dinsmore)</h4>
<h4 class='h9 m5'>
<a class='' href='http://www.ted.com/talks/scott_dinsmore_how_to_find_work_you_love?language=ko' lang='ko'>
당신이 좋아하는 일을 어떻게 찾을까
</a>
</h4>
<div class='meta'>
<span class='meta__item'>
Posted
<span class='meta__val'>
Sep 2015
</span>
</span>
<span class='meta__row'>
Rated
<span class='meta__val'>
Inspiring, Persuasive
</span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
